1.1
log
@First stab at an armish bootloader.  It will load /bsd from the drive in the
upper slot of the Thecus n2100.  Glued together from bits from the NetBSD
cobalt and evbarm ports.
@
text
@d1 1
a1 1
/*	$OpenBSD$	*/
@

